Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.30,0:00:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在被星光照射的顶屋里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.90,0:00:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,独自一人聆听着天空的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.55,0:00:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用玻璃的绷带遮住眼睛行走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.20,0:00:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是孤独的马戏团孩子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.85,0:00:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孤身一人的悲伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.10,0:00:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,震动的绷带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.87,0:00:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撼动着心灵……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.35,0:01:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用温柔的眼神期待与某人的相会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.05,0:01:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在我耳边细语“请留在我身边”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.27,0:01:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Silent Voice

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.32,0:01:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,镇压亚古捷斯的古利明舰队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.69,0:01:37.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与姬娜的舰队开始交战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.37,0:01:40.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随着战斗空域广大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.49,0:01:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新亚加码陷入了危机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.21,0:01:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,此时程为盾牌的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.90,0:01:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是一直想与布拉度舰长见面的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.65,0:01:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艾美莉代理舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.11,0:01:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我犯下不可挽回的大错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.39,0:01:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第四十五话\N亚古捷斯的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.09,0:02:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姬娜已率领友军舰队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.34,0:02:21.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去亚古捷斯去讨伐古利明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.96,0:02:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在其后方支援
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.70,0:02:28.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目标是成为\N夺回亚古捷斯的先锋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.44,0:02:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可小看敌人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.18,0:02:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亚古捷斯的新人类部队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.93,0:02:34.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,远比高达队伍更强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.89,0:02:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,安多拉的勇者们啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.89,0:02:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了获得勇者名声
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.50,0:02:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任何人也不可\N对古利明军手下留情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.83,0:02:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算对手是你过去的战友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.80,0:02:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命运一定会给哈曼大人\N带来辉煌的胜利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.46,0:02:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恶有恶报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.45,0:02:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,罪恶必受惩罚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.79,0:02:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种情况的洗脑作业\N倒是做的很好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.26,0:03:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恶有恶报,犯罪必受惩罚...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.65,0:03:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要欺骗自己人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.13,0:03:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就必须先与自己人同化
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.85,0:03:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会输的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.79,0:03:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果说这是肮脏的血统\N我也只好承认了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.22,0:03:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是下次见面时\N我一定要取下你的人头
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.09,0:03:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用我这双手来重建吉翁王国
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.16,0:03:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧,哈曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.63,0:04:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球联邦军的援军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.56,0:04:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎不打算进入三号殖民地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.81,0:04:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他们想渔翁得利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.13,0:04:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个空域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.99,0:04:19.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已被我们新人类的意识控制了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.34,0:04:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般人不会进来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.20,0:04:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说的对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.99,0:04:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家听着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.96,0:04:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉翁的士兵啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.28,0:04:30.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,临终的时刻已过了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.13,0:04:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,万恶的根源就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.35,0:04:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夺走美莉芭殿下的哈曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.34,0:04:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能掌握新吉翁的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.89,0:04:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是将哈曼的人头献上来给我的各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.69,0:04:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到时你们将成为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.78,0:04:50.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,后代口中的宇宙英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.33,0:04:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个黄毛小子真会演讲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.94,0:04:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要我们拿哈曼的人头吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.38,0:04:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思是要给我们一个殖民地了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.18,0:04:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说要给我们地球呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.23,0:05:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很喜欢你啊,古利明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.01,0:05:03.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是在讨你欢心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.62,0:05:07.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对于昨天还对哈曼誓忠的人\N至少要有送他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.06,0:05:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个地球的觉悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.60,0:05:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想把我们的机器人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.19,0:05:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涂成那么难看的颜色吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.63,0:05:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是古利明大人的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.09,0:05:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说为了新吉翁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.97,0:05:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们要团结在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.08,0:05:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想压制浮动的士气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.31,0:05:25.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个主意是不错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.15,0:05:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是,我是例外的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.32,0:05:33.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接给古利明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.43,0:05:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,达卡恩大人要与你谈话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.27,0:05:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.76,0:05:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.59,0:05:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.50,0:05:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了,达卡恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.79,0:05:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多宾野狼\N的确是只有我军才有的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.29,0:05:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随便你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.43,0:05:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小事随时可能会弄死人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.42,0:06:01.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然这么在意外表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.02,0:06:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别撞上摄影机啊,比查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.53,0:06:16.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.49,0:06:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从拉比安罗兹回收过来的零件\N快点修理好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.41,0:06:22.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在做了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.09,0:06:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仓库已经满了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.84,0:06:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在不装上去以后会很难收拾的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.00,0:06:30.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在干脆丢掉吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.86,0:06:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,米莉的意思是那些都是必需品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.25,0:06:34.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.79,0:06:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这些东西在战斗时只会碍事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.94,0:06:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说呢,奇斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.63,0:06:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:41.10,0:06:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉比安罗兹的黑盒子\N一定要找到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.74,0:06:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里有艾美莉代理舰长\N生前的最后遗言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.72,0:06:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我正在找啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.13,0:06:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,黑盒子太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.70,0:06:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这个吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.43,0:06:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,录有艾美莉声音的磁片
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.95,0:07:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请放心吧,艾美莉代理舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.54,0:07:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会交到\N布拉度舰长手上的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.84,0:07:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,空气有点沉重
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.06,0:07:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是空调故障了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.52,0:07:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候还说笑\N你这是什么个性啊?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.00,0:07:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是不可小看的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.61,0:07:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别再说了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.42,0:07:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫迪,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.14,0:07:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我问你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.91,0:07:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,悲伤就能让死人复活的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.09,0:07:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过去的事情早点忘记是好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.78,0:07:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人一死就完了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.35,0:07:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.76,0:07:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我们以后我们还得活下去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.58,0:07:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这种人最容易早死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.35,0:07:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊,莫迪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.55,0:07:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,百式的维修工作还没好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.17,0:07:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我等一会再去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.37,0:07:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫迪不可能不伤心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.82,0:08:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也刚失去重要的人啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.45,0:08:02.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是说拉莎拉吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.28,0:08:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说不定他比米莉更伤心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.35,0:08:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫迪,捷度呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.49,0:08:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他说等一会过来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.90,0:08:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自己的MS
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.09,0:08:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不自己照顾可以吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.57,0:08:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莫迪那小子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.46,0:08:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们不能太指望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.31,0:08:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地球联邦的援军
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.72,0:08:35.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古利明下次从亚古捷斯出来时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.23,0:08:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他会当作没看见\N我们去打哈曼吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.94,0:08:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.01,0:08:41.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以那时候\N我们从侧面攻击古利明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.07,0:08:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然后再战哈曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.73,0:08:45.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只能瞄准旗舰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:45.54,0:08:46.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.05,0:08:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吉翁开始活动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.00,0:08:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是哈曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.30,0:09:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对  哈曼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.26,0:09:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在把古利明当成敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.03,0:09:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但没人能保证\N哈曼会再艘船上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.83,0:09:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但也没人能保证\N哈曼不在那里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.82,0:09:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总之不管怎样\N哈曼必定会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.45,0:09:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全力攻击亚古捷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.86,0:09:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们只能从后面追上去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.59,0:09:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在后面旁观战况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.60,0:09:23.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能知道哈曼打的主意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.07,0:09:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错,哈曼在那艘船上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.70,0:09:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.55,0:09:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度到底支持哪边的?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.24,0:09:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道吗?\N捷度想和哈曼做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.34,0:09:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后的了结啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.43,0:09:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后的了结?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.20,0:09:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思是某一方会死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.25,0:09:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的想法太极端了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.43,0:10:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.52,0:10:07.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古时候的日本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.44,0:10:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,军人出阵前会远离身边的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.54,0:10:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,与自己的武器共渡一夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.03,0:10:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起,阿斯兰治
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.08,0:10:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天怎么这么老实的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.34,0:10:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是新装甲吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.53,0:10:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,这是把浮走粒子做成漆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.16,0:10:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,重复烤漆好几层的装甲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.06,0:10:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,光波击中它会被反弹开的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.67,0:10:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是光波若是持续三秒以上\N漆就会融化掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.35,0:10:34.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.51,0:10:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目标是新吉翁军的宇宙要塞\N亚古捷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.78,0:10:38.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.93,0:10:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.83,0:10:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再放出假陨石吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.90,0:10:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别发呆\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.33,0:11:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我叫你们别发呆啊\N快跟我走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.57,0:11:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.47,0:11:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道吧,尼伊,蓝斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.35,0:11:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.31,0:11:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躲在假陨石的后面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.78,0:11:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,胆小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.14,0:11:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样做不成大事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.93,0:11:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,达卡恩,急于立功会出错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.93,0:11:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.92,0:11:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是要拿下古利明人头的\N是我马士文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.84,0:11:59.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,洗脑很成功啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.10,0:12:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,听着,安多拉的勇者们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.30,0:12:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天这一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.62,0:12:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是新吉翁的最佳一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.71,0:12:23.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古利明是叛徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.52,0:12:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是坏蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.40,0:12:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家跟随我去打倒他吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.65,0:12:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈曼大人忠实的仆人\N去开出血路吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.62,0:12:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要让哈曼看清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.59,0:12:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古利明不是我的对手的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.21,0:12:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我感觉到力量了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.97,0:12:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这场仗我赢定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.40,0:13:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久没那么痛快了,看我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.83,0:13:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,避开啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.44,0:13:27.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这两架MS是姬娜的亲卫队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.11,0:13:30.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,该死的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.21,0:13:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,坏一架\N应该是达卡恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.32,0:13:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看我多宾野狼的厉害吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.65,0:13:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.94,0:13:41.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.59,0:13:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩这个把戏吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.94,0:13:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧,小鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.63,0:13:51.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躲的真快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.14,0:13:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这点程度不算什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.10,0:13:59.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要自大啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.10,0:14:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?这是什么压力?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.55,0:14:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是从哪里来的?那里吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.91,0:14:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姬娜吗?不,不是\N是马士文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.29,0:14:34.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然不要命的跑出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.19,0:14:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不知道害怕的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.64,0:15:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马士文挺能打的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.03,0:15:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你玩了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.99,0:15:08.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙不是常人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.43,0:15:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很难分出胜负
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.61,0:15:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看来会变成长期战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.96,0:15:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分出结论了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.94,0:15:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈曼是认真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.49,0:15:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也帮忙击败亚古捷斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.54,0:15:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不然背后受到攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.55,0:15:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好,准备战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.93,0:15:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全体各就各位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:44.41,0:15:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度,走吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.34,0:15:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.37,0:15:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.17,0:15:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.49,0:15:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很惹人厌吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.58,0:15:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:58.01,0:16:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比查你怎会这么好心\N肯和我说话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.61,0:16:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我平常也是这样的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.53,0:16:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.64,0:16:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是某人过去的心不在身上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.19,0:16:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才没有注意到的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.26,0:16:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.53,0:16:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种话我不会说两次的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.92,0:16:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧,艾莉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.40,0:16:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去吧,大家都在等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.21,0:16:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个...活着回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.23,0:16:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再对我说一次好吗?比查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.97,0:16:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,代理舰长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.89,0:16:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发射假陨石
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.47,0:16:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,掩护高达队伍出动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.81,0:16:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.40,0:16:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能活着回香格里拉吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.86,0:16:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你能的,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.14,0:16:54.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,莉娜,谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.79,0:16:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?ZZ高达
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.24,0:16:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,发动OK
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.93,0:17:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,达卡恩吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.57,0:17:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姬娜,给我看看你的本领吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.81,0:17:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别像你手下那样逃跑啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.47,0:17:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.74,0:17:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,了不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.92,0:17:55.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的背上没有光波炮吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.12,0:17:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你太天真了,达卡恩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.95,0:18:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姬娜,你没事吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.60,0:18:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.63,0:18:15.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度,好久不见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.77,0:18:19.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,捷度,你为何要救我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.64,0:18:22.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么?姬娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.47,0:18:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.60,0:18:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好像听到捷度的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.63,0:18:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了? 姬娜\N又来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.39,0:18:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姬娜大人,你没事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.70,0:18:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,废话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.02,0:18:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,猫女姬娜怎么可能被打败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:34.51,0:18:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是ZZ高达怎么会再那里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.82,0:18:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是来还上次的人情债啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.26,0:18:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很记恩的嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.22,0:18:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又来了,又传来捷度的声音了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.34,0:18:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姬娜大人,你怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.96,0:18:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了\N别大声叫啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.24,0:18:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会头痛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.71,0:18:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪里?姬娜大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:51.83,0:18:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我头痛了,别管我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.74,0:18:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?姬娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.68,0:18:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你害的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.95,0:19:00.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里\N姬娜大人就不对劲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.31,0:19:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波蕾二世被压制了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.64,0:19:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要一口气冲进去吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.14,0:19:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.41,0:19:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,古利明还没使出全力啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.80,0:19:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要假装撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.48,0:19:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,引出他的战力吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.15,0:19:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你上当了\N马士文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.15,0:20:00.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种骗小孩的玩意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.21,0:20:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会让你干脆死掉的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.02,0:20:09.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别担心\N下手吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.54,0:20:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被弹回了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:18.11,0:20:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你动了什么手脚?马士文
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.88,0:20:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不会失败的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.48,0:20:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会战到死为止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.50,0:20:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快脱离啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:40.82,0:20:42.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哈曼大人万岁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.29,0:20:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么光芒?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.36,0:21:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?是谁死了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.70,0:21:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马士文吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.80,0:21:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马士文死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:13.48,0:21:16.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来出去时的气势\N只是装出来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.04,0:21:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,强化过头了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.38,0:21:29.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样我就少掉一个\N可以随意控制的棋子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.43,0:21:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姬娜大人,你要去哪里?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.41,0:21:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马士文死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.63,0:21:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来了!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.47,0:21:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,同一招对付不了那个驾驶员的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:43.89,0:21:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么办?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.09,0:21:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,撤退!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.39,0:21:47.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,休想逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:50.41,0:21:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姬娜,回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.82,0:21:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要替马士文报仇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:53.62,0:21:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是命令,立刻回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.18,0:21:58.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敌人就在眼前啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.84,0:22:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.14,0:22:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?这是怎么回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.43,0:22:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.65,0:22:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事?

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.30,0:22:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成百 成万 上亿的繁星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.49,0:22:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为何只是闪耀而已 展示你言语的能力吧 
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.55,0:23:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我也能不回头地 让心灵出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.70,0:23:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若能把多如繁星的生命储存的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.65,0:23:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把整个银河也化作光芒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:19.35,0:23:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,化作紧握在掌心的 生命的重量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.32,0:23:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我仍未能看见宇宙的路标
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:34.22,0:23:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,手掌触摸着一千万年的光芒

Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.49,0:23:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,MS战不利的古利明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.62,0:23:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,试图用亚古捷斯和哈曼的舰队碰撞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.15,0:23:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也要与古利明和波蕾二世对决
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:55.46,0:23:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是被他们两个压制住了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.77,0:23:59.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波蕾来救我了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.35,0:24:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不对 是波蕾二世？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:01.85,0:24:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下集 高达ZZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.97,0:24:04.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,共震
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.68,0:24:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波蕾二世 太勉强了！
